{"tid":1003064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[之前話唔用華為會落後5G建設] 德國電訊提安全建議 有條件接納華為5G","createTime":"2019-01-31T11:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T12:11:53.000Z","uid":116572,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eaea38ee6c355adb42027e3455dfa2a58b3e44a7","tid":1003064,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"德國電訊提安全建議 有條件接納華為5G<br />\n<br />\n歐洲最大電訊公司德國電訊(Deutsche Telekom)提出一系列措施，確保在國家安全不受威脅的情況下，容許中國電訊設備供應商，包括華為集團，仍有機會參與德國的5G網絡建設。<br />\n自從美國政府發出警告，指華為的電訊設備裝有「後門」，可進行網絡監察後，德國政府在柏林舉行首次高級別會議，磋商是否阻止華為的產品進入當地電訊市場，會後提出該項建議，相信有助華為突破美國政府的遏制政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/2050925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2050925&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=893cf1f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/2050925</a>"},{"pid":"d2b0a65c8b90ed8af812fbb5551cf46723df5719","tid":1003064,"uid":116572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"德國電訊警告禁用華為將輸5G競賽<br />\n<br />\n德國電訊在一份內部評估報告中稱，若政府因安全隱憂而禁止使用華為的產品，歐洲將會在部署5G網絡的競賽中，被美國和中國拋離。<br />\n外電引述知情人士表示，德國電訊的高層已發出警示，若從5G供應商名錄中剔除華為，將令歐洲推出5G技術的時間至少滯後兩年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/2049238/德國電訊警告禁用華為將輸5G競賽\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2049238%2F%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%B0%87%E8%BC%B85G%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BD&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=e2f11942\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/2049238/德國電訊警告禁用華為將輸5G競賽</a>"},{"pid":"15339a3af39925ada42ce057cc8766bf16f36a45","tid":1003064,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"連登無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}